{"id":149215,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/德国向东欧开放就业市场-加强黑工检查力度/","date":"2011-05-01T21:30:25Z","modified":"2011-05-02T01:21:53Z","title":"德国向东欧开放就业市场 加强黑工检查","content":"<div>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">柏林</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">5月1日开始，德国的就业市场向8个东欧和中欧地区的欧盟成员国开放。这8个国家是波兰，匈牙利，捷克，斯洛文尼亚，斯洛伐克以及爱沙尼亚，拉脱维亚和立陶宛。罗马尼亚和保加利亚暂时还无法享受</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">“</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">就业者来去自由</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">”</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">的条例。德国劳工部长冯德莱恩(Ursula von der Leyen)及德国财政部长朔伊布勒都表示, 要加强对黑工以及超低工资的检查力度。</span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a href=\"http://fulltextrssfeed.com\"><img src=\"http://fulltextrssfeed.com/images/1x1.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"ftrf - full text rss\" /></a><a href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C15042869%2C00.html%3Fmaca%3Dchi-rss-chi-all-1127-rdf&#038;title=%E5%BE%B7%E5%9B%BD%E5%90%91%E4%B8%9C%E6%AC%A7%E5%BC%80%E6%94%BE%E5%B0%B1%E4%B8%9A%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA+%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%BA%E9%BB%91%E5%B7%A5%E6%A3%80%E6%9F%A5%E5%8A%9B%E5%BA%A6\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hid